      "tags": ["documentation", "workflow", "agent-instructions", "project-intelligence", "entry-point"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "以 project-intelligence:start/end 注释包裹的受控指令块，明确区分执行工具与工作流层，并要求 finish/maintain 的 --task 参数使用中文。"
    },
