      "name": "SKILL.md",
      "filePath": ".claude/skills/gitnexus/gitnexus-refactoring/SKILL.md",
      "summary": "GitNexus 重构技能文档，提供 rename、extract、split 三类重构的 checklist，结合 rename 多文件改名与 detect_changes 验证作用域，并列出风险缓解规则。",
      "tags": ["documentation", "gitnexus", "refactoring", "skill", "workflow"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:.npmignore",
      "type": "file",
      "name": ".npmignore",
      "filePath": ".npmignore",
      "summary": "npm 发布忽略清单，排除 __pycache__、.pyc 缓存、plugins/project-intelligence/tests 测试目录与 .DS_Store，避免将 Python 缓存与测试打进发布包。",
      "tags": ["configuration", "build-system", "npm", "ignore-patterns"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "config:.project-intel/config.json",
      "type": "config",
      "name": "config.json",
      "filePath": ".project-intel/config.json",
      "summary": "Project Intelligence 工具配置，定义扫描 include/exclude 范围、quality 测试命令、backend 入口识别规则，以及后端分层、API、配置、权限、事务、远程调用等 inferred 级规则。",
      "tags": ["configuration", "project-intelligence", "scan-config", "quality-rules", "standards"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "rules.inferred 以中文描述后端 Controller→Service→Repository 分层、权限/事务/远程调用/错误码等约定，并附带 evidence 证据计数。"
    },
    {
      "id": "config:.project-intel/graph/project-graph.json",
      "type": "config",
      "name": "project-graph.json",
      "filePath": ".project-intel/graph/project-graph.json",
      "summary": "Project Intelligence 合并图谱摘要，记录 GitNexus 与 Understand-Anything 两个图谱源的状态、统计与角色，汇总组件/API/服务数量与项目领域分布。",
      "tags": ["configuration", "project-intelligence", "graph-summary", "data-source", "metadata"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "schemaVersion 2，GitNexus 源标记 present 而 Understand-Anything 标记 missing，projectDomains 给出 scanner、tests 两个项目派生领域及代表文件。"
    },
    {
      "id": "config:.project-intel/manifest.json",
      "type": "config",
      "name": "manifest.json",
      "filePath": ".project-intel/manifest.json",
      "summary": "Project Intelligence 项目清单，记录 schema/tool 版本、git 提交与分支、框架、包名、文件与后缀计数、图谱源状态与工具链 (node/gitnexus/understandAnything) 可用性。",
      "tags": ["configuration", "project-intelligence", "manifest", "metadata", "project-context"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "包含 git.dirty 标志、suffixCounts 后缀分布统计与 graphSources 双图谱源声明，notes 用中文提示优先使用图谱来源。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:.ua/.understandignore",
      "type": "file",
      "name": ".understandignore",
      "filePath": ".ua/.understandignore",
      "summary": "Understand-Anything 分析忽略清单，使用 gitignore 语法排除 OS/编辑器噪声、Python 与 Node 构建产物、VCS 与工具数据目录、测试夹具与锁文件，并保留 evals/skill-behavior-scenarios.json。",
      "tags": ["configuration", "ignore-patterns", "tooling", "understand-anything"],
      "complexity": "simple",
      "languageNotes": "支持 ! 取反强制包含，优先级高于内置默认；显式排除 .ua/、.gitnexus/、.project-intel/cache 等工具自身数据目录。"
    },
    {
      "id": "config:.ua/config.json",
      "type": "config",
      "name": "config.json",
      "filePath": ".ua/config.json",
      "summary": "Understand-Anything 工具配置，设置 outputLanguage 为 zh，使生成的图谱文本内容输出为中文。",
      "tags": ["configuration", "understand-anything", "localization", "tooling"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:bin/project-intel.mjs",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "project-intel.mjs",
      "filePath": "bin/project-intel.mjs",
      "summary": "Node CLI 入口 shim，定位包内 plugins/project-intelligence/scripts/project_intel.py，按平台候选 python3/python/py 依次 spawnSync 调用并透传参数与退出码，缺失或无 Python 时报错退出。",
      "tags": ["entry-point", "cli", "shim", "node", "launcher"],
      "complexity": "simple",
      "languageNotes": "纯顶层命令式脚本无函数声明，使用 spawnSync 同步调用 Python 实现，Windows 下优先尝试 py -3。"
    }
